[
  {
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 7.0,
    "text": "And we welcome for Splendent in a Tartan Kilt. Yes indeed."
  },
  {
    "start": 7.0,
    "end": 11.0,
    "text": "Mr. Ron Burgundy, I won't even ask if you're wearing anything underneath those kilts or that kilt."
  },
  {
    "start": 11.0,
    "end": 14.0,
    "text": "Well, you know, the usual answer is you're not."
  },
  {
    "start": 14.0,
    "end": 17.0,
    "text": "But I'm wearing a usual Speedo."
  },
  {
    "start": 17.0,
    "end": 19.0,
    "text": "Oh, very nice."
  },
  {
    "start": 19.0,
    "end": 22.0,
    "text": "What brought you here to our Roar of the Rings?"
  },
  {
    "start": 22.0,
    "end": 24.0,
    "text": "I was stuck at the airport."
  },
  {
    "start": 24.0,
    "end": 26.0,
    "text": "So are you familiar with this game at all?"
  },
  {
    "start": 26.0,
    "end": 30.0,
    "text": "I am very familiar."
  },
  {
    "start": 30.0,
    "end": 33.0,
    "text": "I was the only one down in San Diego that used to cover curling."
  },
  {
    "start": 33.0,
    "end": 35.0,
    "text": "Push it hard."
  },
  {
    "start": 35.0,
    "end": 41.0,
    "text": "And then you worked a little bit with Glenn Howard and his team, and this was your first stone."
  },
  {
    "start": 41.0,
    "end": 43.0,
    "text": "There it is."
  },
  {
    "start": 43.0,
    "end": 45.0,
    "text": "And you made the 12-foot."
  },
  {
    "start": 45.0,
    "end": 46.0,
    "text": "You didn't even slide."
  },
  {
    "start": 46.0,
    "end": 47.0,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "start": 47.0,
    "end": 48.0,
    "text": "That was my goal."
  },
  {
    "start": 48.0,
    "end": 51.0,
    "text": "I was trying to make it to the 12-foot, and look what happened."
  },
  {
    "start": 51.0,
    "end": 55.0,
    "text": "Because this is all about the Olympics, and by next Sunday we'll know the two Olympic teams that will represent our country."
  },
  {
    "start": 55.0,
    "end": 56.0,
    "text": "Two Olympic teams."
  },
  {
    "start": 56.0,
    "end": 57.0,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "start": 57.0,
    "end": 58.0,
    "text": "One men's."
  },
  {
    "start": 58.0,
    "end": 59.0,
    "text": "One men's team."
  },
  {
    "start": 59.0,
    "end": 60.0,
    "text": "One women's team."
  },
  {
    "start": 60.0,
    "end": 61.0,
    "text": "And an alternate team?"
  },
  {
    "start": 61.0,
    "end": 62.0,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "start": 62.0,
    "end": 63.0,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "start": 63.0,
    "end": 64.0,
    "text": "That's it?"
  },
  {
    "start": 64.0,
    "end": 65.0,
    "text": "Okay, that's it."
  },
  {
    "start": 65.0,
    "end": 66.0,
    "text": "That's it."
  },
  {
    "start": 66.0,
    "end": 67.0,
    "text": "I know that."
  },
  {
    "start": 67.0,
    "end": 70.0,
    "text": "Eight human beings representing Canada in Sochi."
  },
  {
    "start": 70.0,
    "end": 71.0,
    "text": "In curling."
  },
  {
    "start": 71.0,
    "end": 72.0,
    "text": "In curling."
  },
  {
    "start": 72.0,
    "end": 73.0,
    "text": "In curling."
  },
  {
    "start": 73.0,
    "end": 74.0,
    "text": "This is it."
  },
  {
    "start": 74.0,
    "end": 75.0,
    "text": "This is it."
  },
  {
    "start": 75.0,
    "end": 76.0,
    "text": "This is all about this."
  },
  {
    "start": 76.0,
    "end": 77.0,
    "text": "This one throw."
  },
  {
    "start": 77.0,
    "end": 78.0,
    "text": "Right here?"
  },
  {
    "start": 78.0,
    "end": 79.0,
    "text": "No, no, no."
  },
  {
    "start": 79.0,
    "end": 80.0,
    "text": "Oh, gosh, you got me so nervous, Nick."
  },
  {
    "start": 80.0,
    "end": 81.0,
    "text": "I thought it was this one throw."
  },
  {
    "start": 81.0,
    "end": 82.0,
    "text": "No, it wasn't."
  },
  {
    "start": 82.0,
    "end": 83.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 83.0,
    "end": 84.0,
    "text": "And this is the one I like the best."
  },
  {
    "start": 84.0,
    "end": 85.0,
    "text": "The stretchy arrow."
  },
  {
    "start": 85.0,
    "end": 86.0,
    "text": "The stretchy arrow."
  },
  {
    "start": 86.0,
    "end": 87.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 87.0,
    "end": 89.0,
    "text": "They went down here, and then they went down there."
  },
  {
    "start": 89.0,
    "end": 90.0,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "start": 90.0,
    "end": 91.0,
    "text": "And then there's a whole bunch of them you can try."
  },
  {
    "start": 91.0,
    "end": 92.0,
    "text": "And then there's the..."
  },
  {
    "start": 92.0,
    "end": 93.0,
    "text": "That's the..."
  },
  {
    "start": 93.0,
    "end": 94.0,
    "text": "And you can draw the..."
  },
  {
    "start": 94.0,
    "end": 95.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 95.0,
    "end": 96.0,
    "text": "That's the..."
  },
  {
    "start": 96.0,
    "end": 97.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 97.0,
    "end": 98.0,
    "text": "That's the really crazy arrow."
  },
  {
    "start": 98.0,
    "end": 99.0,
    "text": "That's a tougher shot."
  },
  {
    "start": 99.0,
    "end": 100.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 100.0,
    "end": 103.0,
    "text": "Now, I saw this shot once completed in 72."
  },
  {
    "start": 103.0,
    "end": 107.0,
    "text": "A few hills on that ice."
  },
  {
    "start": 107.0,
    "end": 108.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 108.0,
    "end": 109.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 109.0,
    "end": 110.0,
    "text": "But it blew my mind."
  },
  {
    "start": 110.0,
    "end": 111.0,
    "text": "That's right."
  },
  {
    "start": 111.0,
    "end": 112.0,
    "text": "And let's be honest."
  },
  {
    "start": 112.0,
    "end": 113.0,
    "text": "Yes?"
  },
  {
    "start": 113.0,
    "end": 115.0,
    "text": "Because I'm a journalist, and I have to ask the hard-hitting questions."
  },
  {
    "start": 115.0,
    "end": 118.0,
    "text": "You guys bet a lot up here, don't you?"
  },
  {
    "start": 118.0,
    "end": 121.0,
    "text": "Do you bet on who's going to win and who's going to lose?"
  },
  {
    "start": 121.0,
    "end": 122.0,
    "text": "You know what?"
  },
  {
    "start": 122.0,
    "end": 123.0,
    "text": "That's something we don't talk about."
  },
  {
    "start": 123.0,
    "end": 124.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 124.0,
    "end": 125.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 125.0,
    "end": 126.0,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "start": 126.0,
    "end": 127.0,
    "text": "It's sort of a nudge and a wink."
  },
  {
    "start": 127.0,
    "end": 128.0,
    "text": "I had to ask it."
  },
  {
    "start": 128.0,
    "end": 129.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "start": 129.0,
    "end": 130.0,
    "text": "I had to ask it."
  },
  {
    "start": 130.0,
    "end": 131.0,
    "text": "Linda, are we feeling something right now?"
  },
  {
    "start": 132.0,
    "end": 133.0,
    "text": "I know I am."
  },
  {
    "start": 133.0,
    "end": 136.0,
    "text": "I know this kilt doesn't breathe the way they tell you it's going to breathe."
  },
  {
    "start": 136.0,
    "end": 138.0,
    "text": "It's very sweaty underneath this kilt."
  }
]